{"arkId":"cl010110070","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010110070","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"Bouqueti\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Bouqueti\u00e8re"},{"type":"Autre titre","value":"Jardini\u00e8re \u00e0 deux compartiments"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1775","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 611 - Jean-Fran\u00e7ois Oeben","room":"Salle 611, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1775,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"4e quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle = dernier quart du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Manufacture de Rouen","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3067775"},{"label":"Levavasseur, Marie-Thomas","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Atelier de","dates":[{"date":"1748","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1793","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"C\u00e9ramiste\/potier","authenticationType":"marque (estampilles, poin\u00e7ons...)","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6164","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"jardini\u00e8re","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Jardini\u00e8re de forme rectangulaire en largeur, divis\u00e9e en deux compartiments parall\u00e8les, celui de devant plus bas que celui du fond. Elle est d\u00e9cor\u00e9e du th\u00e8me des Marchands levantins inspir\u00e9 d\u0027un tableau de Claude-Joseph Vernet (1714-1789) diffus\u00e9 par la gravure de Charles-Nicolas Cochin le jeune (1715-1790) et Jacques-Philippe Le Bas (1707-1783). Un groupe de levantins en costume national assistent \u00e0 un emballage et au transport de ballots, au bord de la mer. Dans le bas, une frise de croisillons roses (rouges). Sur chacun des c\u00f4t\u00e9s de la jardini\u00e8re, une autre sc\u00e8ne polychrome avec un paysage lacustre. Les bords lob\u00e9s sont d\u00e9cor\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u0027ext\u00e9rieur de hachures bleues, et \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur de guirlandes de fleurs en cama\u00efeu carmin. Pied orn\u00e9 d\u0027une feuille verte en relief. Les deux tablettes de fa\u00efence, qui recouvraient les compartiments, ont disparu.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Marque en bleu sous le fond : \u0022va vasseur\/ a Rouan\u0022","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"15","displayDimension":"15 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"20,5","displayDimension":"20,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"14","displayDimension":"14 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : fa\u00efence\r\nTechnique : techniques c\u00e9ramique","placeOfCreation":"Rouen (Haute-Normandie = Haute Normandie-\u003ESeine-Maritime = Seine Maritime)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection A. de Bellegarde \u00e0 Rouen, sa vente Paris, 12 d\u00e9cembre 1904 n\u00b0 101. Don Albert Bichet (1840-1920), 1908","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Bellegarde","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Propri\u00e9taire"},{"value":"M. Bichet, Albert","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1908","startYear":1908,"endYear":1908}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9p